• Open source framework
• Used by security professionals
Slide 2: Architecture
text
██ Exploits - Code that breaks in
██ Payloads - What runs after
██ Encoders - AV evasion
██ Auxiliary - Scanners, fuzzers
██ Post - Post-exploitation
██ NOPs - No operation codes
Slide 3: Basic Commands
bash
msf > search exploit
msf > use exploit/...
msf > show options
msf > set RHOSTS x.x.x.x
msf > set PAYLOAD ...
msf > check
msf > exploit
[*] Session opened!
